		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you're using both shadows and descenders, you may want to make the capitals 6 pixels tall.<br /><br />Top left: underlying black-and-white image<br />Top right: 3bpp<br />Bottom left: 2bpp without shadow<br />Bottom right: 2bpp with shadow<br /><br />I've reordered the encoding to ASCII, and in each, rows 7 and 8 are the lowercase with some glyphs slightly enlarged for readability.

		
